THE GAME
--------

  'Tribullation' is a Workbench game where you have to blow up
bubbles of the same colour that are next to each other, on a
triangular shaped game board. The more bubbles that are blown up,
the more points you get. As bubbles blow up, they are removed from
the game board and the bubbles that are located upward fall toward
the empty spaces. To blow up, a bubble must be next to at least
one bubble of the same colour...

  Have fun!

